{"tid":223260,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"寶礦力生啫喱","createTime":"2017-04-30T08:13:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-01T03:14:49.000Z","uid":15141,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"481dfb84762ca94c55079dccc937a27648e5a2da","tid":223260,"uid":15141,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T08:13:26.000Z","msg":"之前1月買左支寶礦力 用口飲過 之後就唔記得左佢嘅存在<br />\n今朝見到佢入面有啲好似啫喱咁嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但啲水變返透明<br />\n有冇巴打知呢啲係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/30/160424_4f03bbb1302c7175430eab87f7e36192.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F30%2F160424_4f03bbb1302c7175430eab87f7e36192.jpg&h=ae8d2982&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/30/160424_c5ab542b1dcab25baa3c28e7e07d18fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F30%2F160424_c5ab542b1dcab25baa3c28e7e07d18fb.jpg&h=26127d50&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13f3eb96b05f3fcc2be1838ab7101b8ed988cc57","tid":223260,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T08:14:45.000Z","msg":"發霉"},{"pid":"08b3301bafd85f0427e2fe6ab9604a5ba7536436","tid":223260,"uid":48426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T08:18:32.000Z","msg":"你口水既細菌不停繁殖"},{"pid":"e05004a3ec1bcf703252cc6ed26919f8a117b98b","tid":223260,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T08:19:57.000Z","msg":"shit"},{"pid":"a623c51c45570c62f5ac76bf62f03c8bf2dd646d","tid":223260,"uid":7943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T08:21:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你口水既細菌不停繁殖</blockquote><br />\n異形<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"965bc0ae9053d89491e5fd7984a12b253957c1d8","tid":223