\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd80307f9c18cc46cbdbe3932b2a6eb5675f6cfe","tid":223260,"uid":55296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:01:28.000Z","msg":"仲啫喱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n擺明係發霉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46041d666f7d788f04921c68e573369403601d92","tid":223260,"uid":88485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:27:24.000Z","msg":"樓主係女"},{"pid":"e8117cb559a04e56309978ac09a03439c2c64b78","tid":223260,"uid":15141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T19:12:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主個口好多菌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加埋寶礦力啲糖分造就一個好理想既環境比細菌生長<br />\n<br />\n樓主真係好毒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實唔係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係我男朋友架<br />\n<br />\n所以啲水變返清係啲細菌已經食曬啲糖分？<br />\n如果我繼續加糖有冇機會繼續養佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4608b3b579fc462e7f2de92144abbaffa41584","tid":223260,"uid":15141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T19:15:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主係死肥仔1.5L用口飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個陣病左諗住都要成支隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ed1778955d0471119d3bea8da11520ba5389fc6","tid":223260,"uid":15141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T19:19:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你口水既細菌不停繁殖</blockquote><br />\n諗住繼續放係到 睇下會唔會生滿成樽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你估下個樽會唔會爆</blockquote><br />\n如果佢地keep住生 我估個密度會越黎越高 最後變到好似火龍果汁咁嘅色<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但未到爆"}]}